  "synopsis": "The very last moment before the novel was about the end... The strongest villain met a pitiful fate. But that wasn't the end.\n\n*\"So, this is how I die.\"*\n\nI, who was once the author, woke up as the fox-eyed villian who was never once understood. A fallen family. A life thrown away for revenge. A future sealed in tragedy. I'm going to rewrite it all. This villain's end... will be reversed.\n\n(Source: KakaoPage, translated)",
